# Project-wide rpmlint filters for staging/.
#
# Each addFilter() pattern is matched as a regex against rpmlint's full output
# line. Use this file for warnings that are deliberately accepted across the
# entire repo; per-package quirks should go in a sibling .rpmlintrc next to
# the affected spec instead.

# Many of these packages are leaf binaries or pre-built artefacts with no
# upstream test suite, or the test suite requires network/hardware that mock
# can't provide. We deliberately omit %check rather than ship an empty one.
addFilter("no-%check-section")
